/**
 * ---
 * category: utilities
 * ---
 * Converts a hyphenated string to camel case
 *
 * Example inputs:
 *  - 'foo-bar'
 *  - 'baz-qux'
 *
 * Example outputs:
 *  - 'fooBar'
 *  - 'bazQux'
 *
 * @module camelize
 * @param {String} str
 * @returns {String} Returns camel cased string
 */
description:
Converts a hyphenated string to camel case

Example inputs:
 - 'foo-bar'
 - 'baz-qux'

Example outputs:
 - 'fooBar'
 - 'bazQux'
name: camelize
title: camelize
